item.title: CVE-2023-30522|2024-08-02T14:28:51.817Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20fogbugz%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Fogbugz Plugin 2.2.17 and earlier allows attackers with Item/Read permission to trigger builds of jobs specified in a 'jobname' request parameter.
